    <abstract>
      <t>This document specifies the data model and the overall structure for a framework to provision Session Establishment Data (SED) into Session Data Registries and SIP Service Provider (SSP) data stores.  The framework is called the "Session Peering Provisioning Framework" (SPPF).  The provisioned data is typically used by network elements for session establishment.</t>
